title: Republicans widen Senate majority; House in balance
description: Republicans are nearing a narrow victory in the US House of Representatives, with control hanging on the outcome of a handful of remaining races. While Democrats flipped two New York seats, Republicans are projected to secure a Senate majority, bolstering Trump's agenda. However, a potential slim House majority could limit Trump's legislative ambitions.

title: Putin praises Trump, says Russia ready for dialogue; prez-elect hints they will speak
description: Russian President Vladimir Putin congratulated Donald Trump on his election victory and commended his courage during a past assassination attempt. Putin expressed a willingness to resume dialogue with the Trump administration, acknowledging Trump's campaign remarks on Ukraine and US-Russia relations. However, Putin's spokesman clarified that Russia's stance on Ukraine remains unchanged.
